dsDescriptionValue.value: Masks for the Milky Way Bone filaments used in Zucker, Battersby, & Goodman 2018 (submitted). Original characterization of the Milky Way Bones can be found in Zucker, Battersby, & Goodman 2015. The masks entitled "Fil_mask.fits" are the same masks shown in the green contours in section 6.3.4 in the Appendix, derived via a column density threshold. The masks entitled "Fil_IRDC_submask.fits" are specific subregions of the dust emission based masks, corresponding to the most prominent extinction feature in the filament.
